    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>An outbuilding containing an oven used for baking bread. May be combined with a brewery or other functional structures. May be found associated with farmhouses, hospitals, monasteries, or other major structures.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
